          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The sources of error has several categories-",
                "pure systematic errors consist only of the absolute",
                "Ge-detector efficiency(+-3%) and the solid angle of the",
                "monitor detectors(+-1%).",
                "Pure random errors include the number of counts in the",
                "monitor detector and the reproducibility of the monitor",
                "system in different runs and is +-2%. The main",
                "additional source of error was the absolute X-ray",
                "intensities  and the corrections for summing of",
                "coincidental radiations is 3%.",
                "A summation in quadrature of random and partially",
                "random errors yields a standard deviation of 8.4%."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                ".The corresponding value for purely systematic",
                " errors is 3.2%."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                ".By summing in quadrature the different sources",
                "of error (see above) adopted an error of 10% for each",
                "cross section was reported."
              ]
            },
